Package: check-ice2
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Nagios plugin to check if a ICE or Shoucast stream status
 It is a Nagios plugin to check if a ICE or Shoucast stream status. It started as a fork of pozar/check_ice by Tim Pozar but ended with a full rewrite. designed as a drop-in replacement for check_ice, with some additionnal features :
 - IPv6 support
 - ICY name checks
